261
00:22:12,916 --> 00:22:15,250
You mean another Dragon Ball?

262
00:22:16,625 --> 00:22:17,583
Above!

263
00:22:24,875 --> 00:22:27,958
What's that?! It's not
like any bird I've seen.

264
00:22:38,833 --> 00:22:41,916
[NARRATOR] The Turtle Hermit's
greatest fear has been realized.

265
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:44,666
King Piccolo
has found Goku first!

266
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:47,125
Can Goku survive
against such an

267
00:22:47,208 --> 00:22:49,500
overwhelmingly
powerful adversary?

268
00:22:49,583 --> 00:22:52,625
Find out on the next
action-packed adventure

269
00:22:52,708 --> 00:22:54,458
of Dragon Ball!

